title: How to Cope With Rejection in Dating with Kait Warman
description: Hi ya'll! Rejection... we've all been there, and let's be honest, it hurts. So for today's episode, I brought on Kait Warman to talk aaalllll about rejection, where the feelings stem from, and how to cope with the feeling to then lead with action. Hope that it helps some of you!
